article: amman , jan. ## -lrb- xinhua -rrb- jordanian foreign minister salaheddin al-bashir on monday received here visiting russian envoy for peace process in the middle east alexander sultanov and urged russia to pressure israel into halting aggression and military operations in gaza strip .
abstract: jordan urges russian to exert more pressure on israel to stop its aggression on gaza
